premise_source_doc_sentence: Andrew Gertler  (  born November 8 , 1988  )  is an American talent manager that represents Island Records recording artist Shawn Mendes , as well as Rick Ross 's Maybach Music Group / Atlantic Records recording artist Rockie Fresh .
